text: US Koroki is a Togolese football club based in Tchamba. They play in the top division in Togolese football. Their home stadium is Stade Maman N'Danida.Koroki champion à une journée de la fin du championnat. ==Achievements== *Togolese Championnat National: 1 ::2018 ==References== Category:Football clubs in Togo
